### ❌ Don't Ignore Type Safety

```aria
// BAD: Incompatible types
string:bad = user?.age ?? "Unknown";  // ❌ int64 ?? string

// GOOD: Convert types explicitly
string:age = toString(user?.age) ?? "Unknown";
```

