## Mutable Captures

### Single Mutable Capture

```aria
fn make_toggle() -> fn() -> bool {
    state: bool = false;

    return || {
        $state = !$state;  // Toggle state
        return $state;
    };
}

toggle: fn() -> bool = make_toggle();
stdout << toggle();  // true
stdout << toggle();  // false
stdout << toggle();  // true
